    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 ">
        <h2 class="visible-xs">Getting the most from your cleaner</h2>
    </div>
    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
        Communication is the key to getting a great cleaning service. On our App you can leave instructions when you book a cleaner online. We also recommend that you show your cleaner around your
        property so you can explain what house cleaning you’d like them to do.
    </div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
        It is always good to tidy up your home before your scheduled clean. You don’t want to waste precious cleaning time! Your housekeeper’s time is best spent doing cleaning tasks rather than picking up clothes or toys or tidying up magazines. This also helps ensure that their
        time does not run out before finishing the cleaning.
    </div>
    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 ">
        <h2 class="visible-xs">What to expect from your house cleaner</h2>
    </div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
        A sparkling home! You can also expect your cleaner to be trustworthy,
        reliable, punctual and honest.
    </div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
        A routine regular cleaning service includes a thorough cleaning of kitchens and bathrooms, vacuuming and
        mopping throughout the house, dusting all surfaces and making beds.
    </div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12">
        You may want some extras like ironing, oven cleaning, fridge cleaning or window cleaning.
        Simply click these options when you book a cleaner through our App.
    </div>
    <div>&nbsp;</div>

